	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Curacao</placeName> <date>13 February 1858</date>&#8212;</p>
				<p><addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
				<p>Reverend Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">With none of your to reply too I. <sic>reffer</sic>.<lb/> to my last of the <date>16 December</date> Ulto which I hope have rea&#44;&#44;<lb/>ched you <sic>safed</sic> together with &#36;68&#44; <sic>remetted</sic> to the of <persName>Messrs<lb/> Dovale &#38; Co.</persName> <placeName>N&#47;Y.</placeName> I have this pleasure again to day of<lb/> sending you to the care of said Gentlemen forty dollars<lb/> which I have collected from a few friends as donation<lb/> for the new <sic>Sinagoge</sic> <hi rend="underline">Beth El</hi> of your place&#44; this<lb/> sum have not been <sic>remetted</sic> before&#44; because I have<lb/> been absent from home for some times&#59; donation sh&#44;&#44;<lb/>ould&#44;&#44; have been liberal by every members here&#44; if it was<lb/> not for so many subscription&#44; donation&#44; and loans&#44;<lb/> which were given during last year&#44; but any how I<lb/> hope this will be accepted.  The exhibition I mention&#44;&#44;<lb/>eted you in my last Shall be upon on the <date>19 April</date><lb/> next&#44; the benefit of the same shall be <sic>destributed</sic><lb/> between the three communities&#44; Israelites&#44; Protestant&#44;<lb/> and Catholics&#59; a commission of directors is appointed <persName>Rev&#58;<lb/> Choemaceiro</persName> is chosen as President&#44; <persName>Mr Mehyer</persName> Pro&#44;&#44;<lb/>testant minister vice P. <persName>Mr Kickens</persName> Catholic mi&#44;&#44;<lb/>nister <sic>Serc</sic>.&#59; and <persName>Mr D. Senior Jr</persName> Treasurer this plan<lb/> has been invented by <hi rend="underline">Haham</hi>&#59; I shall have the<lb/> pleasure of communicate you the result of it<lb/> afterwards&#59; <sic>Pleace</sic> to give this to your readers&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I am very truly yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">B. de Cafferes Jr</persName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p><addressee>Rev&#58; Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
		</body>
